India is the seventh largest country in the world.
India belongs to the continent of Asia, it is bordered by the countries of Bangladesh, Bhutan, Burma, China, Nepal, and Pakistan.
In the Hindu calendar, there are six seasons or ritus: vasant Ritu (spring), grishma ritu (summer), varsha ritu (monsoon), sharad ritu (autumn), hemant ritu (pre-winter), and shishir or shita Ritu (winter)
